br />\n<br />\n就係知啱啱開始多人湊熱鬧先遲d 去睇<br />\n咁又有得屌<br />\n成個展覽得你睇得？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 我都想講依樣<br />\n仆街 佢一開既平日已經去左 已經打撚晒蛇餅<br />\n七月八月 都去左二次度 都係咁多人<br />\n有心睇就六月去 真係難聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a410e9e6b9b3fa3492a7b6c39a59ee92cb2cdd37","tid":437900,"uid":5085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T18:38:24.000Z","msg":"有心睇既，6月開既時候就去排係值得尊重 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但事實上真係識玩既，一定係暑假o岩o岩完、又未到十一黃金週既9月去&hellip;&hellip;冇紅日既日子想搵蛇餅打都難 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fceda00c337138c824ee4680e21c59fca4de4a2","tid":437900,"uid":3535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T18:49:08.000Z","msg":"六月睇都已經好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905a1efdceeaac7b3ebe0c89d517f6be89e310c5","tid":437900,"uid":128830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T18:59:27.000Z","msg":"今日真係好多人<br />\n根本乜都睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fca449f2d56a2506c8047a68228675da02bde36","tid":437900,"uid":8829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T19:05:40.000Z","msg":"咩鐘數會少人啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"d634d4c6b84d5d2bbde9298b95e8fb8a340f9d5a","tid":437900,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T19:14:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩鐘數會少人啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n察係朝早啦，仲駛問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62fcfe81fd593c667386b61f02e97bbb90ac5acd","tid":437900,"uid":17104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T20:49:04.000Z","msg":"咩叫有心去就6月開個陣去<br />\n岩岩開就俾新假期報左多人到仆街 等遲啲再去都叫港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n唔通個個去都要同你講我係黎學野架 我有興趣知埃及文化先唔叫港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實今次個展覽做得幾好 尤其一入去段片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲文字解說令唔同年齡既人都可以好易就明佢啲歷史同文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去大英博物館睇可能因為我英文廢 睇啲字郁用左好多時間理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"018aa604e10a139fdee4d4b3c579b98861d8a302","tid":437900,"uid":14898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T21:38:16.000Z","msg":"？？？<br />\n叫香港人唔去睇？留比中國人睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去睇下學下野都有錯？而家搞喪禮咩尊重尊重，人地展品嚟咋⋯就算做雞都唔可去睇嘅咩"},{"pid":"1999e9df8aafde4b220a0267527454b026040d00","tid":437900,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T23:59:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話說有博物館通行證可以直入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果次我去太空館申請完就去科學館睇mummy，唔洗排直入<br />\n太空館完全冇人排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對面歷史博物館都無人排<br />\n果次去科學館排長龍買飛<br />\n立即轉去對面出全年證<br />\n比多20就唔洗排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91fbd21dd489a6f245b59038bb949c24d2e6d781","tid":437900,"uid":92065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T00:22:24.000Z","msg":"屌！上次去乜撚都睇唔到！<br />\n淨係可以透過人地部電話個cam去睇"},{"pid":"0c9f0d5289bb3336791f4836442a35f65a7ea175","tid":437900,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T01:00:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去當地大英博物館、羅浮宮又咪大把人影<br />\n得香港人好似當影相有罪咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一世人去旅行當地博物館我諗都係得幾次啫下話,留個記念回憶無問題<br />\n但實情班港豬港女有幾多係認真看待個展覽?<br />\n男既,當左係拍拖勝地 入到去同條女攬頭攬頸<br />\n女既,首先個衣著已經好搞笑,著到成隻雞咁入去比Mummy定比女睇<br />\n我唔係講笑,班女入到去狂影相,又嘻嘻哈哈 真係CLS</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/nvgl2e5u\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnvgl2e5u&h=e0b05e44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你真係覺得冇問題?</blockquote><br />\n一世人去大英博物館、羅浮宮咪又係得果幾次<br />\n博盡無悔呀嘛<br />\n香港科學館你幾乎日日去都得</blockquote><br />\n一世人會有乜機會科學館有木乃伊睇"},{"pid":"f84e310e62512fafd31e25851d377f5fb4f9e379","tid":437900,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T01:04:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>個展覽本身6月開始,正常有心睇嘅晨早就去睇左。。。<br />\n<br />\n就係知啱啱開始多人湊熱鬧先遲d 去睇<br />\n咁又有得屌<br />\n成個展覽得你睇得？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得既,笑柒你港豬囉</blockquote><br />\n有舒服唔去嘆,係要等人多逼晒先黎慢慢去,害人又害己<br />\n咁撚鍾意逼日日6~7點去金鐘站慢慢逼囉</blockquote><br />\n我第一日請假去照係多人<br />\n暑假唔洗諗啦<br />\n根本早去遲去都係多"},{"pid":"b7a5725df33dd19f7cbcbddd300429f771beff8d","tid":437900,"uid":22743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T01:06:58.000Z","msg":"早一兩個月去 人唔多 好好睇 睇左兩個幾鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  睇到都唔知時間 啲首飾好靚"},{"pid":"19d7df952317d98e256ec27add4918346ddb92a3","tid":437900,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T01:07:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港嘅展覽真係做得好好，解說都做得好足</blockquote><br />\n無錯,但係好多香港人完全唔尊重個展覽同Mummy<br />\n班Mummy山長水遠由埃及黎香港 比班港豬係咁影影影<br />\n我懷疑其實班港豬龍友上身,影Mummy係假,偷影長腿索爆大波港女至真</blockquote><br />\n埃及黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3177590164fb304cd6d855f3b997c3f7abad172","tid":437900,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T01:38:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>四月係大英睇過<br />\n七月係香港睇過<br />\n老老豆豆香港做得更好 (係資源提供方面)<br />\n<br />\n人既話 跟本不相伯仲<br />\n大英咪一樣照樣埃及果section極多人<br />\n相機食先<br />\n相反古希臘少人得多<br />\n米索不達米亞果邊人都無個<br />\nIslam world剩係得Muslim入去...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日本館直頭天堂<br />\n係得返真係對日本文化有興趣嘅鬼佬慢慢睇<br />\n感覺似番個博物館"},{"pid":"8017c346b65d13c6f90436b58b65d5ab1c85960d","tid":437900,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T01:43:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>mummy 都想睇下女姐...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMummy: 我喺倫敦睇慣唔少金髮靚女遊客，個個波大大籮翹翹，又肯露，不知幾撚爽。香港啲蔗渣板？No la <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9268e5b527ff3c613b1c75cd0d78651d3a13360","tid":437900,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T02:37:54.000Z","msg":"連登仔真宇宙警察<br />\n之前有post 直情話影相都唔應該<br />\n仲話去呢啲不如去大英睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"218bb12b2212a90e721c93a61b85eda4c66029c1","tid":437900,"uid":39200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T03:17:13.000Z","msg":"樓主自己睇完啦就唔想比人睇<br />\n<br />\n仲唔係仆街仔?"}]}